[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    643[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    644[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mLinda's vignette is the chapter's strongest opening. The clinical specificity (HFrEF EF 35%, T2DM A1c 8.4%, CKD 3b eGFR 38, AFib on apixaban), the operational specificity (240,000 members, 18,000 eligible, 1,400 slots, top 8% by predicted admission risk, 41% 12-month admission probability), the social context (lives alone in fourth-floor walkup with temperamental elevator, daughter at 90 minutes' distance, two specific recent admissions with the in-retrospect signals, the metformin-not-adjusted-for-eGFR detail in the lucky-version closing), and the explicit unlucky-versus-lucky contrast is the most directly contrarian opening in the chapter.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    645[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"Both versions of Linda's story are real. The first version is, regrettably, more common."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m The dual-narrative-with-acknowledgment closing is the chapter's clearest articulation of the gap between dashboard-success and outcome-success.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    646[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Six wrinkles framing is the recipe's central pedagogical structure: program slots are limited and expensive, programs have theories of change, response prediction is harder than risk prediction, ROI math is regulatory and contractual, care management is rationing, enrollment is not one-time. The numbered-wrinkles structure is heavy but works because each wrinkle is genuinely distinct and cumulative.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    647[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The recommender picks. The LLM packages."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m Same single-line framing as 4.5 and 4.6, applied to the highest-stakes packaging surface in the chapter.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    648[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The thing that surprises people coming from generic ML backgrounds is how much of the work is operational, not modeling. ... A program with an excellent uplift model and poor operations under-delivers. A program with mediocre modeling and excellent operations over-delivers. The order of investment is operations first, modeling second."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m The 25/75 framing is the chapter's clearest articulation of where care-management programs actually spend their time.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    649[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The thing I'd do differently the second time: invest in the post-graduation observation pathway before the initial enrollment optimization."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m The personal-confession-with-explicit-ordering framing is exactly the CC voice the chapter rewards.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    650[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"Last point, because it's specific to this use case: care management is rationing, and rationing decisions in healthcare deserve more rigor than retail recommendation decisions."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m The closing explicit-ethics paragraph is the chapter's most direct ethics framing yet.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    651[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The "we'll do randomization later" trap explicitly named: [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"Two years later they still haven't randomized. ... Don't accept 'no randomization' as the durable state; it's the worst version of the program's measurement."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m This is operational-veteran framing.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    652[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The "highest-risk-first" reflex under capacity contraction explicitly diagnosed: [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The mathematical reality is that under capacity constraint, the patients you should prioritize are the ones with highest uplift, which is not necessarily the highest-risk patients. ... Have it explicitly, with the math, with the cohort instrumentation."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m This is the kind of mathematical-versus-political framing that distinguishes the recipe.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    653[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Em dash check: 0 (verified). En dash check: 0 (verified). 70/30 vendor balance: clean. Marketing-language scan: two borderline "high-leverage" hits (lines 818 and 1798), both colloquial uses meaning "leverage point," consistent with 4.6's voice.[K
